    <item>
      <title>被赫格斯解雇的海军上将晋级决选以取代梅斯</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/nancy-lacore-mace-south-carolina.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南希·拉科雷 (Nancy Lacore) 将在 2021 年选区面临一场艰难的秋季选举，该选区将更加支持共和党。她正在寻求取代众议员南希·梅斯，后者竞选州长失败，而不是竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/nancy-lacore-mace-south-carolina.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·希尔顿 (Steve Hilton) 击败汤姆·斯泰尔 (Tom Steyer) 在加州州长竞选中赢得第二名</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/steve-hilton-california-governor-xavier-becerra.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[得到特朗普总统支持的共和党人史蒂夫·希尔顿(Steve Hilton)将在大选中对阵民主党人泽维尔·贝塞拉(Xavier Becerra)。另一位民主党人汤姆·斯泰尔(Tom Steyer)不会晋级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/steve-hilton-california-governor-xavier-becerra.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:47:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独立议员凯文·凯利 (Kevin Kiley) 将在加州众议院竞选中对阵理查德·潘 (Richard Pan)</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/pan-ho-kiley-california-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯利先生今年早些时候放弃了共和党身份。人们普遍认为新划分的第六国会选区对民主党有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/pan-ho-kiley-california-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
